{"type":null,"faqId":43847,"title":"与其他蓝牙设备连接不上的可能原因？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;color:black;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:0.7875in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{text-indent:0.8854167in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">手机能够支持A2DP,HSP,HFP,PAN,HID,OPP,PBAP等profile；若确认连接设备也支持这些profile但仍无法连接，请参考以下情形：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">一、无法搜索到其他手机</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">解决办法：请确认其他手机蓝牙是否已经打开，并已经处于可被搜索状态。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">二、无法搜索到蓝牙耳机</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">解决办法：</span><span>请确认耳机已经处于可被搜索状态（进入配对模式），不同蓝牙耳机进入匹配模式的操作方法不完全相同，相关设置请参考耳机的使用手册或在互联网上寻找解决方案，一般来说，红灯和蓝灯交替闪烁时为可匹配模式</span><span class=\"s1\">。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">三、发送文件时提示无法与其他手机连接</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">解决办法：请确认其他手机是否支持接收文件，或者是否支持接收该类型的文件。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9348","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442399557000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10","visitedTimes":4,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"蓝牙耳机,连接不上","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}